/>\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=c44fa38d\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=ae51c0eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"02e41d82c9982af121eb2e23a71fdea7a0dec270","tid":1672222,"uid":265731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"So99y呢單所謂嘅新聞真係信唔落，仲要係西班牙警方搜到？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00dfd5f2007209f3a4b6b820367dfba6ae6ba553","tid":1672222,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:39:48.000Z","msg":"都話唔好去架la"},{"pid":"cb6e31a0f0fa8e8befa534bb5624f8cfda3ab8f4","tid":1672222,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:44:25.000Z","msg":"真 打著紅旗反紅旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"